Personal Energy Footprint


Specify a date range to generate visualization:        

  • Personal Footprints
  • Comparison Pie Chart
  • Real-time Footprint
  • Note

The footprint service allows the user to query and visualize the energy footprint data in several formats, as demonstrated here.

The personal energy footprint is generated by combining user's location data with the energy consumption history at each location; the statistics were calculated using historical data, while real-time footprint is also available.

Historical data here were collected around December 2015.
